text: Stępków is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dębowa Kłoda, within Parczew County, Lublin Voivodeship, in eastern Poland. It lies approximately west of Dębowa Kłoda, south-east of Parczew, and north-east of the regional capital Lublin. ==References== Category:Villages in Parczew County
title: Stępków
